Holder is a talented musician<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> who has recorded a number of albums; <it>Black London Blues</it> (1969), <it>Bootleg Blues</it> (1971), <it>You Simply Are...</it> (1975)<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref> and <it>Ram Blues &amp; Soul</it> <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%224%22])">4</ref>.  He has also released various singles and contributed to soundtracks for film and television, including three songs for the film adaptation of <it><literary_composition wordnetid="106364329" confidence="0.8">
<written_communication wordnetid="106349220" confidence="0.8">
